Favicons

These sample favicons have been generated at http://realfavicongenerator.net/.

To add your own simply visit http://realfavicongenerator.net/ and generate a new set of favicons (change the path option to /favicons/) and replace all of the files in this folder. Then update the favicon section in the head.html include with the generated meta tags.
